# SDK Package Guidelines

The SDK package provides client libraries for integrating with the ErrorHub API.

## Structure

- [packages/sdk/core](mdc:packages/sdk/core) - Core functionality and interfaces
- [packages/sdk/browser](mdc:packages/sdk/browser) - Browser-specific implementation
- [packages/sdk/node](mdc:packages/sdk/node) - Node.js implementation with Fastify plugin

## API Design

- Keep the public API simple and intuitive
- Provide type definitions for all public methods
- Follow Promise-based design for asynchronous operations
- Support caching mechanisms for error messages

## Error Handling

- Handle network errors gracefully
- Provide fallback mechanisms for offline scenarios
- Log appropriate diagnostic information
- Use TypeScript discriminated unions for error types
